<h1>Authentication Resources</h1>

<p>Authentication resources enable you authenticate users via <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-login/">Facebook</a> or <a href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/persona/">Mozilla Persona</a>.</p>

<p>The following table lists the authentication resources.</p>

<table>
<thead><tr>
<th>HTTP Method</th>
<th>URI pattern</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>POST</code></td>
<td><code>/_facebook_token</code></td>
<td>Facebook</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>POST</code></td>
<td><code>/_persona_assertion</code></td>
<td>Persona</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</doc>
